    <body>
      <div type="transcription" xml:id="transcription_aad_0057" xml:lang="de">
        <div type="envelope">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00231/" ed="1r" type="envelope"/>
          <ab hand="#hand_blue_auden" xml:lang="en">
            <lb/>A<hi rend="underline" hand="#hand_blue_auden">ir-Mail</hi>
          </ab>
          <ab hand="#hand_blue_auden" xml:lang="en">
            <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">W<unclear>.</unclear>H<unclear>-</unclear>Auden</rs>
            <address>
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
              <lb/>New York City
              <lb/>New York 10003
              <lb/>U.S.A.</rs>
            </address>
          </ab>
          <ab hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Her<unclear>r</unclear>n
            <lb/>Hugo Kurka</rs>
            <address>
              <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_356">Wien XX
              <lb/>Adalbert Stiftergasse 22/28
              <lb/><foreign xml:lang="en">Austria</foreign></rs>
            </address>   
          </ab>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00232/" ed="1v" type="envelope"/>
        </div>
        <div type="letter">
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00233/" ed="2r" type="sheet"/>
          <div type="letter_message" hand="#hand_blue_auden">
            <opener>
              <dateline xml:lang="en">
                <date>
                  <lb/>Nov 13<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
                </date>
                <placeName>
                  <address>
                    <lb/><rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
                    <lb/>N.Y.C<unclear>.</unclear>
                    <lb/>N.Y. 10003</rs>
                  </address>
                </placeName>
              </dateline>
              <salute>
                <lb/>Lieber <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_107">Hugo</rs>.
              </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
              <lb/>Besten Dank für deinen Brief. Die
              <lb/>politische Lage hier is so tr<unclear>a</unclear>urig : ich könnte nicht
              <lb/><rs type="event" ref="#amp_event_id_116">wä<unclear>h</unclear>len entweder für <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_261">Humphr<unclear>e</unclear>y</rs> oder <unclear>f</unclear>ür <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_260">Nixon</rs></rs>.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Ich weiss dass all<unclear><subst><del rend="overwritten" hand="#hand_blue_auden">u</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#hand_blue_auden">e</add></subst></unclear> Küche-Masch<unclear>in</unclear>en sind <unclear>v</unclear>iel
              <lb/>t<unclear>e</unclear>uerer in <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_30">Europa</rs> als in <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_15">Amerika</rs>. Wenn Du und
              <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_240">Christ<gap reason="illegible" unit="char" quantity="1"/></rs> w<subst><del rend="overwritten" hand="#hand_blue_auden">eiss</del><add place="superimposed" hand="#hand_blue_auden">isss</add></subst>en genau was sie brauchen, schreibe mir
              <lb/>so fort und ich schicke <unclear>d</unclear>as Geld.
            </p>
            <p>
              <lb/>Ich bin ein bischen einsam, sonst <del rend="overstrike" hand="#hand_blue_auden">es</del> geht es
              <lb/>mir gan<unclear>z</unclear> gut. Denke oft an Dir.
            </p>
            <closer>
              <salute>
                <lb/>immer dei<unclear>n</unclear> Freund
              </salute>
              <signed>
                <lb/><rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">Wystan</rs>
              </signed>
            </closer>
          </div>
        <pb facs="https://iiif.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/aad/aad_00234/" ed="2v" type="sheet"/>
        </div>
      </div>
